of those dying en route, so more than 1 in 5 not surviving the journey.

00:03:23.575 --> 00:03:26.645
Of those that were lucky enough to survive, they would

00:03:26.645 --> 00:03:29.885
find a life of backbreaking labour ahead of them.

00:03:30.935 --> 00:03:35.495
No doubt for many, there were times that they wished they had not survived the trip.

00:03:36.975 --> 00:03:43.025
It was from the trade of these people, African slaves, that Colston’s riches originated.

00:03:44.575 --> 00:03:49.655
The money might have eventually flowed towards so called “good” causes, in terms

00:03:49.655 --> 00:03:54.715
of hospitals and dwellings for the poor, but the fact that it had come from

00:03:54.715 --> 00:04:00.645
this most inhumane of businesses meant that it was forever tainted, stained by

00:04:00.645 --> 00:04:05.245
the blood and suffering of those who had been sold into slavery to create it.

